name: JONI NIGHTMARE (Night 2)
description: Joni was chilling at his crib whit the homies, everything was cool, untill something too funny happend and Joni started laughing super hard, suddently he touches his mouth and two teeth fall on his hand, he trys to tell the homies and when he articulates a first word he spits out a couple of teeth more... paranoia kicks in and he ran to the bathroom, blood everywhere, all his teeth started falling one by one no stop, seconds after, he sneezes two times, the first time.. his right eye pops out and second time... his left eye pops out. Desperation takes control of him when he looks at himself from his fallen eye, he is scared af, WAKE HIM UP!
